➜时间管理大师，迷恋秦皇汉武：当皇帝也信成功学，会有什么后果？
http://www.sohu.com/a/416907257_624188	32466
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200907/2e731cae5ae04e398e50cc3e7302d679.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">1451年前</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在那个南北方互相瞧不起的时代</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">唐高祖<strong>李渊</strong>的表弟出生了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200907/214fdbb4931348deb1c3c288888572bb.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">当时</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">跟表弟小英的老爸比</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">李渊他爸还只是个<strong>小官</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">更何况</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">小英不但从小聪明长得帅</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还是个<strong>贼能写诗的文科生</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他不但能讨爸妈欢心</p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
<section class="lookall">
<a href="javascript:;" class="show-all" id="showMore">
<em>展开全文</em>
</a>
</section>
</div>
<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-center">还体贴他人</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有一次</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">小英在围猎时下起了倾盆大雨</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">侍卫立即递上<strong>油布衣</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200907/3b8b16de736945c2b7e132465c0f6b05.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">小英<strong>坚持不穿</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">看到将士们都浑身淋湿</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他不好意思独善其身</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">将士百姓知道后都很<strong>感动</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200907/000a3477a41346bea9a5cb36814ad997.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200907/4bbbb8d0bd704f39b4d1572afd86bf8a.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">为此</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">爸妈都很宠小英</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">13岁时</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">送他去安徽江苏当<strong>省长</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还给他相亲讨个南方老婆</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">15岁时</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">让他带<strong>51万兵</strong>打南方的<strong>陈王朝</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">打赢后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">小英斩贪官，封钱库</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不夺百姓钱财</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">成了<strong>江南红人</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200907/22e51f5c32b94aa88973d3c8f4e4e369.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">自此</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">小英立下<strong>Flag</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">既然崇拜<strong>秦皇汉武</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那就要成为他们</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">对了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他后来改名为——</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>杨</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>广</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200907/b8ace456e3ef46cdabe3541d23d5ec4e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200907/3b8b16de736945c2b7e132465c0f6b05.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">50岁时</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他被最信任的臣子<strong>勒死</strong>在皇位前</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">孙子命谥号为<strong>隋明帝</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">却被表哥李渊改为<strong>隋炀帝</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">“炀”听着好听</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">意思可一点都不好听——</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200907/f67068fa8a574a8b8b6ea217daaa8775.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200907/4e2f71c0ae344317855504dadc33dbb5.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">翻过课本都知道</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>京杭大运河</strong>的包工头是隋炀帝</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">当大家在利用大运河发财脱贫时</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也在<strong>纠结</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200907/237d443c73894208b7e947622f3415de.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那么</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就让我们来一探究竟吧——</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200907/38b9a2c79cbd4b678e1216635acc8844.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>有何罪之时间管理者隋炀帝</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">公元604年</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">杨广上位</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">看了皇帝成功学《史记》</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">为了向偶像<strong>秦始皇</strong>看齐</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">年号取为<strong>“大业”</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">发誓要干出一番大事业</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">然后四处出差</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在位15年</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">只在长安宫里呆了不足<strong>4</strong>年</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200907/5cf9e930467b4d9eacf93f601fd56cf5.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">看起来也做了很多业绩</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200907/3b8b16de736945c2b7e132465c0f6b05.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">15年后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">趁着农民起义</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">表哥带领着<strong>瓦岗军</strong>一起讨伐隋炀帝</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">按照惯例</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">要写一篇檄文</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">证明自己是<strong>合法篡位</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200907/55fdbce9d148475fa95bf75e033bf4b1.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">从此</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">隋炀帝背上了<strong>千古暴君、昏君、淫君</strong>的三合一骂名</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">对于修京杭大运河</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也被归结为<strong>荒废政事、巡幸无度、苛捐杂税</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不可否认</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">为了<strong>政绩</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">隋炀帝<strong>劳民伤财，民不聊生</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这是<strong>治国大忌</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200907/ce46c1c726034e6385a0c3a791e802b4.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200907/0de8da415c8e4a4aaadb9d7ed404a83c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">对于修大运河</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">大家裁定杨广的<strong>动机</strong>是吃喝玩乐加炫富</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>《资治通鉴》</strong>足足用了两百多字</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">控诉他的大运河之旅有多<strong>奢侈</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">以<strong>龙舟</strong>为例</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">足足高四十五尺，长二百丈</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有<strong>一百二十间金玉</strong>装饰的房</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">需要<strong>8</strong>万<strong>纤夫</strong>才能拉得动</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">简直是<strong>移动的宫殿</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">后人发现</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">《资治通鉴》的记载是以<strong>《大业杂记》</strong>为原本的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200907/e8ceadb206d84166bb0cb5219dc3e309.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">《大业杂记》里的船才<strong>长200尺，有160间房</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">200尺相当于60米</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不算上走廊</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">船只有900平方米</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">160间房摊下来</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">平均面积也只有<strong>11.25平方米</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">似乎不够奢侈</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200907/f19fb94716a44de1922cc5535c6fd0b5.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">另外</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">当时杨广南下的专用水道<strong>瘦西湖</strong>只有<strong>八九米宽</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">如果龙舟要在水面上行动自如的话</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那么龙舟的宽度只能<strong>六七米</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">资治通鉴上的船似乎<strong>不能行动自如</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200907/d133c53136e44fe98c0d976fea44c7cd.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">再说回动机</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">据<strong>黄仁宇</strong>研究——</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>其实</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>杨广修大运河也算在继承父亲遗志</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">587年</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>隋文帝杨坚</strong>为了征服江南土地</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">贯通南北</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">开凿了大运河体系里的<strong>淮河</strong>和<strong>长江</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200907/fba2e5b971204d38aa631ffe88e0a7cf.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">开凿结果不太好</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">满足不了军事需求</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">于是杨广拿下了这<strong>接力棒</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200907/6cbfc887d83a4d1eac58a24fbded29e5.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">对当时修河的<strong>百万社畜</strong>来说</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">大运河一点好处都没有</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">累得要死要活</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">可几十年后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">唐朝人民开始体验到大运河赚钱的便利</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>GDP蹭蹭蹭暴涨</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200907/de512cdc637a4c16bd21d602a3571ab5.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>为何被网爆之工具人隋炀帝</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">如今</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有的人了解隋朝</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">主要通过<strong>野史</strong>和<strong>小说</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">借着隋炀帝<strong>三次出差江都</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">各种YY人设</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">正好热搜能力最强的也是这些小说</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">毕竟<strong>爽文吃遍天下</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200907/aadfb848a4b64970a50c02bfdf025a63.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">于是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>《封神榜》纣王</strong>和<strong>《隋唐演义》杨广</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">成了小时候的噩梦</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">长大后</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我们开始看正史了解隋炀帝更多八卦</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200907/57ae3a96479e4512b0dc6fbd7b2741c5.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">唐朝是<strong>从隋炀帝手里夺来江山</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">再加上<strong>玄武门兵变</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">所以</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">到了<strong>李世民</strong>这一代</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">皇权的<strong>合法性</strong>尤其重要</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>魏征</strong>给李世民开了条新路——</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">以史为鉴，特别以隋为鉴</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不能得罪老百姓</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">杨广的错事千万不能再犯</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这才有了<strong>修改过的《隋书》</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200907/b87567dc499b44bd9fbecd7f4af1a907.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">因此</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">出于给统治阶级借鉴的动机</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">杨广是历代皇帝的<strong>错题工具人</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">《隋书》等正史的可靠性会<strong>有所降低</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">夸张成分会多点</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有丑化的嫌疑</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200907/a4086a3b0c214ab5af271724b7db9502.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">关于隋炀帝迁都的原因</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">宋朝《资治通鉴》认为——</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>迷信的杨广听信了术士之言和民间流传的蛊惑之语</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>风水不好，不迁都会灭国</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">唐朝《隋书》却认为——</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>杨广是为了完成父亲南北统一的遗愿</strong></p>
<blockquote class="ql-align-justify">
自隋朝建立之初，便欲以河、洛之地为创业之地，先帝长久思虑挂念此事，一讲起来就令人激动哽咽！朕必完成先帝之志！
</blockquote>
<blockquote class="ql-align-right">
——《隋书》
</blockquote>
<blockquote class="ql-align-justify">
陛下的命属木，而雍州地处破木之冲，不宜久居；且谶语有言‘重建洛阳，恢复晋朝之天下’！
</blockquote>
<blockquote class="ql-align-right">
——《资治通鉴》
</blockquote>
<p class="ql-align-center">另外</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">专家发现</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">为了突出隋炀帝的恶</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>司马光删除了《隋书》《北史》中</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>隋炀帝的正面资料</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">例如政治经济改革，多达十九处</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还<strong>增加了有疑点的反面资料</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">例如弑父和大运河奢靡生活</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">目前</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">隋炀帝收到最多的反馈是</p>
<blockquote class="ql-align-center">
弊在当代，功过千秋
</blockquote>
<p class="ql-align-center">当然</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">更多人认为他是一无是处的暴君</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">是与非，功与过</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这个天秤目前还在做</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200907/3e5fd1af714c44f4931c30cb7a864e3c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">最终的判断还得看下去</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200907/59269d7030884e3c87837bfe34de1ea1.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有人似乎已经迫不及待报复了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">2014年</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>开发商</strong>在<strong>扬州</strong>挖地</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">正好挖到了隋炀帝的墓</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而这开发商</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">正好是<strong>杨勇</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200907/3f8a2cfadec6488c85fe9bc86ac196ae.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>